item.title: Will the MINI JEEP make it to AREA 51? Ep3: 5 days alone at 10,000ft.
item.description:
PDS Debt is offering a free debt analysis. Make this the year you take control of your debt. It only takes thirty seconds. Get yours at https://PDSDebt.com/c90adventures
Well there we are, the final video of the tank track conversion. Well...until next time (evil laugh).
I hope you enjoyed the chaos in this one, and I meant it, being up on that mountain alone for that long is one of my favourite things I've ever done.
If you'd like to help more videos get made and support the channel I sell merchandise at https://c90adventures.co.uk/shop/ my paypal donation email address is ed.march@c90adventures.co.uk my Patreon is https://www.patreon.com/c90adventures and my Mum appears to support my "career" choice. I think.
Oh and to see a Promo for the lawnmower trip across Nevada (I will also be making my own version here btw), Michael Reeve's Patreon is https://www.patreon.com/michaelreeves He's mental, I love him.
